# 🌦️ Weather Dashboard Application

## Overview

The **Weather Dashboard Application** is a feature-rich weather monitoring system that provides users with real-time weather information, weather forecasts, and historical weather data using external weather APIs. The application presents weather data through an intuitive and user-friendly dashboard, helping users make informed decisions based on current and future weather conditions.

This project demonstrates API integration, data processing, error handling, and user interface design while working with real-world external data sources.

---

## Features

✅ Real-time weather updates

✅ Current temperature, humidity, wind speed, and pressure

✅ 7-day weather forecast

✅ Hourly weather forecast

✅ Historical weather data visualization

✅ City-based weather search

✅ Location-based weather detection

✅ Weather condition icons and descriptions

✅ Temperature unit conversion (°C / °F)

✅ Responsive dashboard design

✅ Error handling for invalid locations and API failures

---

## Technologies Used

### Frontend

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript (ES6)

### Backend (Optional)

* Python (Flask) / Node.js

### APIs

* OpenWeatherMap API
* WeatherAPI
* Visual Crossing Weather API
* Open-Meteo API

### Additional Libraries

* Chart.js (Weather Trends Visualization)
* Axios / Fetch API
* Bootstrap / Tailwind CSS

